<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Rock</title>

<style>

body{
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin:0;
    background:#f4f4f4;
}

header{
    background:#c0392b;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:30px;
}

.container{
    max-width:1000px;
    margin:40px auto;
    padding:20px;
    display:flex;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    gap:20px;
    justify-content:center;
}

.card{
    width:250px;
    background:white;
    border-radius:10px;
    box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    overflow:hidden;
}

.card img{
    width:100%;
    height:180px;
    object-fit:cover;
}

.content{
    padding:15px;
}

h3{
    margin-top:0;
}

p{
    color:#555;
    font-size:14px;
}

.btn{
    display:block;
    width:200px;
    margin:40px auto;
    text-align:center;
    padding:10px;
    background:#c0392b;
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:5px;
}

.btn:hover{
    background:#922b21;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>🎸 Rock</h1>
<p>Um dos estilos musicais mais influentes da história</p>
</header>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501612780327-45045538702b">
<div class="content">
<h3>Queen</h3>
<p>Banda britânica famosa por músicas como Bohemian Rhapsody e We Will Rock You.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507874457470-272b3c8d8ee2">
<div class="content">
<h3>Nirvana</h3>
<p>Banda de grunge dos anos 90 liderada por Kurt Cobain.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497032205916-ac775f0649ae">
<div class="content">
<h3>AC/DC</h3>
<p>Uma das maiores bandas de hard rock da história.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

<a href="/musicas" class="btn">⬅ Voltar para estilos</a>

</body>
</html>